Kxb7 14. Qf3+ c6 {A logical answer, fighting for space.} (14... Kb8 {is also
possible.} 15. Bg3 e5 16. O-O-O Qe6 17. Qc6 (17. d5 Qg4 18. Qxg4 Nxg4 19. h3
Ngf6 $11 {The white bishop is strongly restricted by Black's pawns.}) 17... Nh5
18. Ne4 (18. dxe5 $2 {Curiously, this seemingy innocuous move puts White into
