e3 Nbd7 9. Bd3 {This is the most active way to develop the bishop, preparing
e3-e4.} h6 10. Bh4 g5 11. Bg3 h5 12. h4 {Once again the principled plan.} (12.
h3 Ne4 13. Bxe4 {A necessary concession in order to keep the kingside intact.}
(13. Bh2 g4 {Due to the hanging pawn on g2, White is forced to sacrifice the
