Nxg3 14. fxg3 Qe7 15. O-O g4 16. Be4 O-O-O 17. Bxb7+ Kxb7 18. Nh4 Rhg8 19. Kh2
Kb8 20. a4 Qg5 21. a5 gxh3 $15 {Jung,R (2198)-Sanchez,A (2296) ICCF email 2014
