15. Qa4 (15. Qc2 Qe7 16. b4 c5 17. Qb2 Rc8 18. dxc5 bxc5 19. b5 Rd8 20. Ne4 e5
21. Ng5 Nf8 22. O-O-O Ne6 $17 {Ree,H (2500)-Hort,V (2585) Arnhem/ Amsterdam
1983 (0-1, 54)}) 15... Qe7 16. O-O-O Kd8 $5 $146 {The same plan as in the
mainline. Other moves offer White more chances to prove his compensation.} (
16... e5 17. Bf5 {Mascaro March,P (2414)-Schnelzer,R (2230) Barcelona 2015 
(1-0, 33)}) (16... a6 17. Kb1 e5 18. Rc1 O-O-O 19. b4 {, with a certain
