Black is quite active and White's extra pawn does not count for much.}) (14. a4
{is an attempt to stabilize the queenside.} Rac8 (14... Nb8 $6 {is premature.}
15. d5 $1 Na6 16. Ng5 e5 {Salem,A (2624)-Moiseenko,A (2692) Berlin 2015 (1-0,
